# 07.07 Enterprise Product

## Overview

The Enterprise Product defines how cmdOS provides AI-powered execution capabilities for organizations.

While personal users use cmdOS to automate individual tasks, enterprises require a secure, scalable, and controllable AI execution platform that can operate across complex business environments.

cmdOS Enterprise transforms AI from a productivity assistant into an intelligent digital workforce.

Core principle:

Business Intent

