# 1. Enterprise Product Purpose

The purpose of cmdOS Enterprise is to provide organizations with an AI Execution Operating System that can:

- Automate business workflows
- Connect enterprise systems
- Create specialized AI Agents
- Improve operational efficiency
- Enable secure AI adoption

